{"type":"text","timestamp":1775870659541,"sessionID":"ses_285de6bdaffeSCYlWS06GqDtjM","part":{"id":"prt_d7a23af6a001DuftPFaDv7eaVO","messageID":"msg_d7a2396850012Ophl3NpoecveV","sessionID":"ses_285de6bdaffeSCYlWS06GqDtjM","type":"text","text":"## AR-023: CLI invoke/status 命令 - Archive Summary\n\n### ✅ What Was Completed\n\n**Core Implementation:**\n- **InvokeRuntime** (`agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`): Fully implemented with 92% test coverage\n  - Supports both agentcube and k8s providers\n  - JSON payload validation and custom headers\n  - Session management with session_id headers\n  - Async HTTP client integration (httpx)\n  - Comprehensive error handling and logging\n\n- **StatusRuntime** (`agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`): Fully implemented with 100% test coverage\n  - Supports both agentcube (AgentRuntime CR) and k8s (Deployment/Service) providers\n  - Multi-provider status checking\n  - Detailed status information (replicas, ready_replicas, endpoints)\n  - Graceful error handling for missing deployments\n\n**CLI Integration:**\n- Both commands fully integrated in `agentcube/cli/main.py`\n- Complete parameter validation and help text\n- Rich console output with progress indicators\n- Verbose mode support\n\n**Testing:**\n- 49 unit tests (all passing)\n- Excellent code coverage (92% for invoke, 100% for status)\n- Tests cover: initialization, validation, provider switching, error handling, edge cases\n\n**Documentation:**\n- README.md updated with invoke/status usage examples\n- Comprehensive design.md (1136 lines)\n- Detailed tasks.md (1034 lines with 71 planned tasks)\n\n### ⏸️ What Was Deferred\n\n**Integration & E2E Testing:**\n- Integration tests with real providers (Tasks 19-22)\n  - `tests/integration/test_invoke_agentcube.py`\n  - `tests/integration/test_invoke_k8s.py`\n  - `tests/integration/test_status_agentcube.py`\n  - `tests/integration/test_status_k8s.py`\n- End-to-end workflow testing (Task 23)\n  - Complete pack → build → publish → invoke → status workflow\n\n**Advanced Test Scenarios (Tasks 24-48):**\n- Offline scenario testing (network failures, DNS issues)\n- Concurrent invocation testing\n- Large payload handling (>1MB, deeply nested JSON)\n- Special characters and Unicode handling\n- Performance testing under load\n- Edge cases and boundary conditions\n\n**Additional Features:**\n- Webhook support for invoke responses\n- Streaming response handling\n- Batch invocation capabilities\n- Advanced status filtering and querying\n- Historical status tracking\n\n**Infrastructure:**\n- Dedicated integration test directory structure\n- Mock HTTP server for invoke testing\n- Test data fixtures for complex scenarios\n- CI/CD integration for integration tests\n\n**Documentation:**\n- Advanced usage examples\n- Troubleshooting guides\n- Performance tuning recommendations\n- Best practices documentation\n\n### 📊 Test Results\n- **49 tests passed**, 5 skipped\n- **Overall coverage**: 38% (includes all CLI modules)\n- **InvokeRuntime coverage**: 92%\n- **StatusRuntime coverage**: 100%","time":{"start":1775870659537,"end":1775870659537}}}
